      gov.nih.nci.cabig.ctms.tools.DataSourceSelfDiscoveringPropertiesFactoryBean

All Implemented Interfaces:
org.springframework.beans.factory.FactoryBean, org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean
public class CaaersDataSourcePropertiesFactoryBean
extends gov.nih.nci.cabig.ctms.tools.DataSourceSelfDiscoveringPropertiesFactoryBean
implements org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean

This class searches through the following directories, looking for a file named ${databaseConfigurationName}.properties:

  • ${catalina.home}/conf/caaers
  • ${user.home}/.caaers
  • /etc/caaers
It loads this file and returns it when DataSourceSelfDiscoveringPropertiesFactoryBean.getObject() is called.

Author:
Rhett Sutphin
